        <mxCell id="oboflow" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=10;html=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;OBO Token Flow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;1. User message triggers tool call&lt;br&gt;2. No cached token → auth_request (WS msg)&lt;br&gt;3. Browser opens OAuth2 PKCE popup&lt;br&gt;4. Agent exchanges auth code + agent credentials&lt;br&gt;5. Asgardeo returns OBO token&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;{ sub: user, act.sub: agent }&lt;br&gt;6. Token injected into API call (hidden from LLM)&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="290" x="55" y="760" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
